name: pandasql
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pandasql" %}
{% set version = "0.7.3" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 1eb248869086435a7d85281ebd9fe525d69d9d954a0dceb854f71a8d0fd8de69

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - python >=3.6
    - sqlalchemy

test:
  imports:
    - pandasql
    - pandasql.tests

about:
  home: https://github.com/yhat/pandasql/
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: "sqldf for pandas"
  dev_url: https://github.com/yhat/pandasql/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - psortos
    - mxr-conda
